}{\plain \fs24 \f1 \tab }{\plain \fs24 \b\f1 122.}{\plain \fs24 \f1   The deeper significance of the word }{\plain \fs24 \i\f1 scoglio}{\plain \fs24 \f1  (slough) is the subject of Lino Pertile's \softline
